  <brief_title>A Study Comparing the Analgesic Efficacy and Safety of Extended Release Hydrocodone/Acetaminophen (VicodinÂ® CR)and Placebo in Subjects With Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Multi-center, Double-blind Study Comparing the Analgesic Efficacy and Safety of Extended Release Hydrocodone/Acetaminophen and Placebo in Subjects With Osteoarthritis</official_title>
